{"metadata":{"symbolKind":"property","title":"useStripeSDK","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"useStripeSDK","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb"},{"text":"?","kind":"text"}],"modules":[{"name":"StripePayments"}],"externalID":"s:14StripePayments27STPSetupIntentConfirmParamsC03useA3SDKSbSgvp","roleHeading":"Instance Property","role":"symbol"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A boolean number to indicate whether you intend to use the Stripe SDK’s functionality to handle any SetupIntent next actions."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If set to false, STPSetupIntent.nextAction will only ever contain a redirect url that can be opened in a webview or mobile browser."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"When set to true, the nextAction may contain information that the Stripe SDK can use to perform native authentication within your"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"app."}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/com.stripe.stripe-payments\/documentation\/StripePayments\/STPSetupIntentConfirmParams\/useStripeSDK-5rght"},"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"useStripeSDK","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb"},{"text":"?","kind":"text"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.stripe.stripe-payments\/documentation\/StripePayments","doc:\/\/com.stripe.stripe-payments\/documentation\/StripePayments\/STPSetupIntentConfirmParams"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/stripepayments\/stpsetupintentconfirmparams\/usestripesdk-5rght"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"kind":"symbol","references":